1412
01:57:18,080 --> 01:57:21,277
What is it? Can I get you something?

1413
01:57:22,480 --> 01:57:26,109
Glass of water.

1414
01:57:26,760 --> 01:57:28,557
Of course, darling.

1415
01:57:29,120 --> 01:57:31,111
I'll be right back.

