1430
02:02:52,680 --> 02:02:56,036
My God, in him will I trust.

1431
02:02:56,240 --> 02:02:59,118
Surely, he shall deliver thee
from the snare of the fowler...

1432
02:02:59,280 --> 02:03:01,635
...and from the noisome pestilence.

1433
02:03:02,080 --> 02:03:05,072
Thou shalt not be afraid
for the terror by night.

1434
02:03:05,240 --> 02:03:07,834
Nor for the arrow that flieth by day.

1435
02:03:08,480 --> 02:03:11,438
Nor for the pestilence
that walketh in darkness.

1436
02:03:11,600 --> 02:03:14,592
Nor for the destruction
that wasteth at noonday.

1437
02:03:15,760 --> 02:03:18,149
He shall cover thee with his feathers...

1438
02:03:18,320 --> 02:03:21,437
...and under his wings shalt thou trust.

1439
02:03:21,800 --> 02:03:26,476
His truth shall be
thy shield and buckler".

1440
02:03:35,400 --> 02:03:38,949
We in this quiet corner of England...

1441
02:03:39,760 --> 02:03:44,231
...have suffered the loss
of friends very dear to us.

1442
02:03:44,840 --> 02:03:47,308
Some close to this church.

1443
02:03:48,760 --> 02:03:53,197
George West, choirboy.

1444
02:03:55,160 --> 02:03:58,994
James Ballard, stationmaster and bell
- ringer...

1445
02:03:59,160 --> 02:04:02,709
...and the proud winner, only
an hour before his death...

1446
02:04:03,160 --> 02:04:07,711
...of the Beldon Cup
for his beautiful Miniver rose.

1447
02:04:09,760 --> 02:04:11,990
And our hearts go out in sympathy...

1448
02:04:12,160 --> 02:04:15,516
...for the two families who share
the cruel loss of a young girl...

1449
02:04:15,680 --> 02:04:19,593
...who was married at this altar
only two weeks ago.

1450
02:04:20,400 --> 02:04:23,358
The homes of many of us
have been destroyed...

1451
02:04:23,520 --> 02:04:26,876
...and the lives of young
and old have been taken.

1452
02:04:27,040 --> 02:04:30,828
There's scarcely a household that
hasn't been struck to the heart.

1453
02:04:31,600 --> 02:04:33,352
And why?

1454
02:04:33,960 --> 02:04:36,997
Surely you must have asked
yourselves this question.

1455
02:04:37,160 --> 02:04:39,913
Why, in all conscience...

1456
02:04:40,080 --> 02:04:42,719
...should these be the ones to suffer?

1457
02:04:43,240 --> 02:04:46,949
Children, old people...

1458
02:04:47,120 --> 02:04:50,795
...a young girl at the height
of her loveliness.

1459
02:04:50,960 --> 02:04:53,758
Why these? Are these our soldiers?

1460
02:04:53,920 --> 02:04:55,478
Are these our fighters?

1461
02:04:56,560 --> 02:04:59,233
Why should they be sacrificed?

1462
02:05:01,960 --> 02:05:04,076
I shall tell you why.

1463
02:05:04,880 --> 02:05:09,635
Because this is not only a
war of soldiers in uniform...

1464
02:05:09,800 --> 02:05:11,597
...it is a war of the people.

1465
02:05:11,760 --> 02:05:13,512
Of all the people.

1466
02:05:13,680 --> 02:05:17,195
And it must be fought not
only on the battlefield...

1467
02:05:17,360 --> 02:05:20,796
...but in the cities
and in the villages.

1468
02:05:20,960 --> 02:05:23,758
In the factories and on the farms.

1469
02:05:23,920 --> 02:05:27,071
In the home and in the heart...

1470
02:05:27,240 --> 02:05:31,153
...of every man, woman and
child who loves freedom.

1471
02:05:31,760 --> 02:05:35,514
Well, we have buried our dead...

1472
02:05:35,680 --> 02:05:37,432
...but we shall not forget them.

1473
02:05:37,600 --> 02:05:42,230
Instead, they will inspire us with
an unbreakable determination...

1474
02:05:42,400 --> 02:05:45,358
...to free ourselves and
those who come after us...

1475
02:05:45,520 --> 02:05:49,672
...from the tyranny and terror
that threaten to strike us down.

1476
02:05:50,400 --> 02:05:52,755
This is the people's war.

1477
02:05:53,080 --> 02:05:55,435
It is our war.

1478
02:05:55,600 --> 02:05:57,875
We are the fighters.

1479
02:05:58,040 --> 02:05:59,314
Fight it, then.

1480
02:05:59,480 --> 02:06:02,278
Fight it with all that is in us.

1481
02:06:02,440 --> 02:06:05,113
And may God defend the right.

